query:
SELECT 
  ja.id,
  CONCAT(c.firstName, ' ', c.lastName) as contractorName,
  ja.startDate,
  ja.endDate,
  ja.notifiedAt,
  ja.acknowledged,
  ja.createdAt,
  j.title as jobTitle
FROM jobAssignments ja
JOIN contractors c ON ja.contractorId = c.id
JOIN jobs j ON ja.jobId = j.id
WHERE CONCAT(c.firstName, ' ', c.lastName) IN ('Mohamed Guizeni', 'Dalwayne Diedericks')
ORDER BY ja.id DESC
LIMIT 5
